# No environment variables are required — this demo is configured AT RUNTIME:
# you enter the tenant + storefront client id on the in-app setup screen.
#
# Optional: prefill the setup form's defaults (handy for local dev). These are
# only used as form defaults; the values you submit are stored in localStorage.
# A storefront client id is PUBLIC (anonymous token, no secret) — never put a
# backend secret here.
#
# VITE_DEMO_DEFAULT_TENANT=acme
# VITE_DEMO_DEFAULT_STOREFRONT_CLIENT_ID=your-storefront-client-id
